Properties.commandText:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[UserId]
    FROM [Artisans] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[EntityStatus] = 'Normal'
) AS [t] ON [o].[ArtisanId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE [o].[EntityStatus] = 'Normal' AND [t].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[Status] <> N'Completed' AND [o].[IsRequestAccepted] = CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT [t0].[Id], [t0].[ArtisanId], [t0].[Cost], [t0].[CustomerId], [t0].[DateCreated], [t0].[DateModified], [t0].[Description], [t0].[EntityStatus], [t0].[IsArtisanComplete], [t0].[IsComplete], [t0].[IsRequestAccepted], [t0].[PaymentMade], [t0].[PreferredCompletionDate], [t0].[PreferredStartDate], [t0].[ReferenceNo], [t0].[RowId], [t0].[Scope], [t0].[ServiceId], [t0].[Status], [t0].[Urgency], [t0].[WorkAddress_City], [t0].[WorkAddress_Country], [t0].[WorkAddress_StreetAddress], [t0].[WorkAddress_StreetAddress2], [t0].[WorkAddress_Town], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[BusinessName], [t0].[DateCreated0], [t0].[DateModified0], [t0].[Description0], [t0].[ECCN], [t0].[EntityStatus0], [t0].[IsApproved], [t0].[IsVerified], [t0].[RowId0], [t0].[Type], [t0].[UserId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[DateCreated], [t1].[DateModified], [t1].[Description], [t1].[EntityStatus], [t1].[Name], [t1].[RowId], [t2].[Id], [t2].[DateCreated], [t2].[DateModified], [t2].[EntityStatus], [t2].[RowId], [t2].[UserId], [t3].[Id], [t3].[DateCreated], [t3].[DateModified], [t3].[DisplayName], [t3].[EntityStatus], [t3].[FamilyName], [t3].[FirstName], [t3].[ImageId], [t3].[IsRemoved], [t3].[IsSuspended], [t3].[IsVerified], [t3].[LevelOfEducation], [t3].[MomoNumber], [t3].[OtherName], [t3].[Password], [t3].[PasswordKey], [t3].[RowId], [t3].[Type], [t3].[Address_City], [t3].[Address_Country], [t3].[Address_StreetAddress], [t3].[Address_StreetAddress2], [t3].[Address_Town], [t3].[Contact_EmailAddress], [t3].[Contact_PrimaryContact], [t3].[Contact_PrimaryContact2], [t3].[Contact_PrimaryContact3]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[ArtisanId], [o].[Cost], [o].[CustomerId], [o].[DateCreated], [o].[DateModified], [o].[Description], [o].[EntityStatus], [o].[IsArtisanComplete], [o].[IsComplete], [o].[IsRequestAccepted], [o].[PaymentMade], [o].[PreferredCompletionDate], [o].[PreferredStartDate], [o].[ReferenceNo], [o].[RowId], [o].[Scope], [o].[ServiceId], [o].[Status], [o].[Urgency], [t].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[BusinessName], [t].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [t].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [t].[Description] AS [Description0], [t].[ECCN], [t].[EntityStatus] AS [EntityStatus0], [t].[IsApproved], [t].[IsVerified], [t].[RowId] AS [RowId0], [t].[Type], [t].[UserId], [o].[WorkAddress_City], [o].[WorkAddress_Country], [o].[WorkAddress_StreetAddress], [o].[WorkAddress_StreetAddress2], [o].[WorkAddress_Town]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[BusinessName], [a].[DateCreated], [a].[DateModified], [a].[Description], [a].[ECCN], [a].[EntityStatus], [a].[IsApproved], [a].[IsVerified], [a].[RowId], [a].[Type], [a].[UserId]
        FROM [Artisans] AS [a]
        WHERE [a].[EntityStatus] = 'Normal'
    ) AS [t] ON [o].[ArtisanId] = [t].[Id]
    WHERE [o].[EntityStatus] = 'Normal' AND [t].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[Status] <> N'Completed' AND [o].[IsRequestAccepted] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ORDER BY [o].[RowId] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[DateCreated], [s].[DateModified], [s].[Description], [s].[EntityStatus], [s].[Name], [s].[RowId]
    FROM [Services] AS [s]
    WHERE [s].[EntityStatus] = 'Normal'
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[ServiceId] = [t1].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[DateCreated], [c].[DateModified], [c].[EntityStatus], [c].[RowId], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Customers] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[EntityStatus] = 'Normal'
) AS [t2] ON [t0].[CustomerId] = [t2].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[DateCreated], [u].[DateModified], [u].[DisplayName], [u].[EntityStatus], [u].[FamilyName], [u].[FirstName], [u].[ImageId], [u].[IsRemoved], [u].[IsSuspended], [u].[IsVerified], [u].[LevelOfEducation], [u].[MomoNumber], [u].[OtherName], [u].[Password], [u].[PasswordKey], [u].[RowId], [u].[Type], [u].[Address_City], [u].[Address_Country], [u].[Address_StreetAddress], [u].[Address_StreetAddress2], [u].[Address_Town], [u].[Contact_EmailAddress], [u].[Contact_PrimaryContact], [u].[Contact_PrimaryContact2], [u].[Contact_PrimaryContact3]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[IsSuspended] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[UserId] = [t3].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[RowId] DESC

FROM [Artisans] AS [a]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[DateCreated], [u].[DateModified], [u].[DisplayName], [u].[EntityStatus], [u].[FamilyName], [u].[FirstName], [u].[ImageId], [u].[IsRemoved], [u].[IsSuspended], [u].[IsVerified], [u].[LevelOfEducation], [u].[MomoNumber], [u].[OtherName], [u].[Password], [u].[PasswordKey], [u].[RowId], [u].[Type], [u].[Address_City], [u].[Address_Country], [u].[Address_StreetAddress], [u].[Address_StreetAddress2], [u].[Address_Town], [u].[Contact_EmailAddress], [u].[Contact_PrimaryContact], [u].[Contact_PrimaryContact2], [u].[Contact_PrimaryContact3]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]

LEFT JOIN (

CREATE TABLE [ConnectRequest] (
    [Id] varchar(36) NOT NULL,
    [InviterId] varchar(36) NOT NULL,
    [InviteeId] varchar(36) NOT NULL,
    [RowId] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [DateCreated] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [DateModified] datetime2 NOT NULL DEFAULT '2023-01-06T19:27:20.9616895Z',
    [EntityStatus] varchar(36) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Normal',
    CONSTRAINT [PK_ConnectRequest] PRIMARY KEY NONCLUSTERED ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ConnectRequest_User_InviteeId] FOREIGN KEY ([InviteeId]) REFERENCES [User] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ConnectRequest_User_InviterId] FOREIGN KEY ([InviterId]) REFERENCES [User] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
